description: Where there is Piti’s Cravings, there’s also likely a long line of foodies waiting patiently for a taste of their divinely flavorful Mexican-Asian fusion cuisine. Among many mouthwatering items on their menu, you will find Popcorn Shrimp Tacos (with irresistibly tasty tempura-fried rock shrimp and Asian white miso), their Kobe Slider (Kobe beef burger with crunchy Hawaiian coleslaw and creamy guacamole), or Sweet Potato Nachos (Fried sweet potatoes topped with a yummy three cheese melt, avocado, and mayo with the perfect kick), to name a few. They have not only raised the bar with their delectable selection, but they’ve made it their mission to raise awareness for pancreatic cancer, using social media to shine a light on ways to make a change. For a dining experience that also benefits the community, come eat at Piti’s Cravings and delight in this “delicious mix of different worlds”.
name: Piti's Cravings
